# Appointment Workflow Overhaul — Walkthrough

## Changes Made

### 1. Double-Booking Detection Fix
- [findExistingAppointment](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/appointment_service.dart#208-224) already correctly filters by `status = "scheduled"` — cancelled appointments won't match
- Added clearer JSDoc comments on the method
- The phone debounce check will only match truly active (scheduled) appointments for the same doctor

### 2. Start Consultation Workflow (replaces premature "Appointment Ended")

**Before:** Patient details filled → card shows "Appointment Ended" immediately

**After (new flow):**
```
Scheduled → Patient Arrived → Fill Details → Start Consultation → [Consultation Form] → Appointment Ended
```

- After patient details are filled, card now shows **"Start Consultation"** button
- Clicking it:
  1. Checks for existing ongoing consultation for the patient
  2. If none → creates a new one
  3. Records `consultation_start_time` on the appointment
  4. Navigates to the ConsultationScreen
- **"Appointment Ended"** only appears after the consultation has been started (`consultationStartTime != null`)

